# GUARDX — Build Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete **8-layer predictive maintenance system** for CNC machines, from data generation to live dashboard.

| Layer | Component | Status |
|-------|-----------|--------|
| 1+2 | Data Simulator (replaces hardware) | 50,000 rows generated |
| 3 | FastAPI Ingestion API | 7 router groups, 20+ endpoints |
| 4 | Preprocessing Engine | Smoothing, outlier capping, 10 features |
| 5 | SQLite Time-Series Storage | 6 tables with WAL mode |
| 6 | ML Intelligence Engine | Isolation Forest + XGBoost, 3-phase lifecycle |
| 7 | Health Score & Risk Engine | Weighted scoring with alert generation |
| 8 | HTML/CSS/JS Dashboard | 6-page SPA with Plotly.js charts |

