## Verification Results

### Dataset Generation
- **50,000 rows** generated successfully
- **70% normal** / **30% fault** distribution across 4 types
- Fault types: bearing_wear, spindle_imbalance, overheating, overload (7.5% each)

### API Testing
```
POST /api/v1/ingest    -> 200 OK (id: 1, timestamp confirmed)
GET  /dashboard/summary -> 200 OK (301 readings, Phase A, score: 0.602)
GET  /ml/status         -> 200 OK (Phase A, IF loaded, 0 labels)
```

### Data Streaming
- 200 rows streamed via [stream_to_api.py](file:///c:/Users/Keerthi%20Sridhar/Desktop/GAURDX/data_simulator/stream_to_api.py) at 0.01s rate
- **0 errors**, 100% delivery

### Dashboard
- All 6 pages render correctly
- Plotly charts populate with live data
- Health gauge, sensor charts, anomaly timeline all functional
- Navigation between pages works smoothly

