## How to Run

```bash
# 1. Generate dataset
python -m data_simulator.simulator --rows 50000

# 2. Start API server
python -m uvicorn api.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000

# 3. Stream data (in another terminal)
python -m data_simulator.stream_to_api --rate 0.1 --max-rows 1000

# 4. Open dashboard
# http://localhost:8000/
```

