35+ files across 7 packages: `data_simulator/`, [api/](file:///c:/Users/Keerthi%20Sridhar/Desktop/GAURDX/dashboard/js/app.js#91-100), `database/`, `services/`, [ml/](file:///c:/Users/Keerthi%20Sridhar/Desktop/GAURDX/dashboard/index.html), [dashboard/](file:///c:/Users/Keerthi%20Sridhar/Desktop/GAURDX/api/main.py#79-86)
